Class Experiment

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.eur.absa.algorithm.Experiment

  • public class Experiment
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class to run experiments with a given Algorithm. Can be used to record outcomes of experiments. Necessary information: - Dataset + config settings - Algorithm(s) -
    Author:
    Kim Schouten
